{"lemma":"جَبَلِ","slug":"جَبَلِ","root":"ج.ب.ل","root_slug":"ج-ب-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-ب-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"جَبَل","root":"جبل","pos":"N","occurrence_count":39},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":8},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n4977","n4978","n4979","n4980","n4981","n4982","n4983","n4988","n4989"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"mountain"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"mountains, mountain range"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to mold, to form, to shape, to fashion"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to knead"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to create"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of جَبَلَ (jabala) (form I); creation"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of جَبَلَ (jabala) (form I); formation"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of جَبَلَ (jabala) (form I); kneading"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare Ugaritic 𐎂𐎁𐎍 (gbl), Biblical Hebrew גְּבוּל (gəḇūl, “border”)."},"ipa":["/d͡ʒa.bal/","/d͡ʒa.ba.la/","/d͡ʒabl/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n4977","headword_ar":"جَبْلٌ","root":"jbl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Big, thick, coarse,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rough;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabilN","text_ar":"جَبِلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", applied to a thing (S, O, K) of any kind: (K:) or this latter is applied to an arrow, signifying (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coarsely, roughly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rudely, pared."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN jabolu Alr~aA^osi","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ جَبْلُ الرَّاْسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA, [in the CK, erroneously,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabalu AlrA^s","text_ar":"جَبَلُ الراس"},{"kind":"text","text":",]) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alwajohi","text_ar":"الوَجْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man having a big, thick, coarse,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rough, head,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"face;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having little sweetness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabiylN","text_ar":"جَبِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN mijobaAlN","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ مِجْبَالٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A big, thick, coarse,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rough, and heavy, man."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 818.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AimoraA^apN jabolapN","text_ar":"اِمْرَاَةٌ جَبْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K [in one place in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabalapN","text_ar":"جَبَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibolapN","text_ar":"جِبْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but only"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabolapN","text_ar":"جَبْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to the TA,]) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mijobaAlN","text_ar":"مِجْبَالٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A woman big, thick, coarse,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rough,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in make;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"large in make."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiloqapN jabolapN","text_ar":"خِلْقَةٌ جَبْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A big, thick, coarse,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rough, make."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 821.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAqapN jabolapu Als~anaAmi","text_ar":"نَاقَةٌ جَبْلَةُ السَّنَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A she-camel having an increasing hump."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sayofN jabolN","text_ar":"سَيْفٌ جَبْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mijobaAlN","text_ar":"مِجْبَالٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sword not made thin."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-  Also (K, TA, [in the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabal","text_ar":"جَبَل"},{"kind":"text","text":",])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A court"},{"kind":"text","text":"[of a house]; syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAHapN","text_ar":"سَاحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"},{"kind":"page_break","n":376}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n4978","headword_ar":"جُبْلٌ","root":"jbl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibolN","text_ar":"جِبْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": ―         -b2-  and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibil~N","text_ar":"جِبِلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Dry trees."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n4979","headword_ar":"جِبْلٌ","root":"jbl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Much;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"numerous;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jubolN","text_ar":"جُبْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) So in the phrases"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAlN jibolN","text_ar":"مَالٌ جِبْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Much property;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"numerous cattle"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaY~N jibolN","text_ar":"حَىٌّ جِبْلٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A numerous tribe."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibil~N","text_ar":"جِبِلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n4980","headword_ar":"جَبَلٌ","root":"jbl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mountain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any of the mountains"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awotaAd","text_ar":"اَوْتَاد"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit. “pegs,” or “stakes,” a term applied to the mountains because they are supposed to make the earth firm, or fast,])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the earth, that is great and long;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, K;) or, as some say, only"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is long;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) such as is isolated being called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^akamapN","text_ar":"اَكَمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qun~apN","text_ar":"قُنَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) [and also applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a rocky tract; any rocky elevation, however little elevated:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and sometimes it means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stone;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rock;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] such, for instance, as is reached by the digger: and hence it is applied to Es-Safà and El-Marweh: (Mgh:) pl. [of mult.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibaAlN","text_ar":"جِبَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K) and (of pauc., Msb)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajobulN","text_ar":"اَجْبُلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajobaAlN","text_ar":"اَجْبَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,] (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man who does not remove from his place:"},{"kind":"text","text":"you say of such a one,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa jabalN","text_ar":"هُوَ جَبَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A niggard."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) [See 4.] ―         -b4-  (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lord,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chief, of a people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"company of men:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"their learned man."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, K, TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abonapu Aljabal","text_ar":"ابْنَةُ الجَبَل"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The serpent:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) because it keeps to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabal","text_ar":"جَبَل"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b6-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Calamity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"misfortune."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b7-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The bow that is made from the tree called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naboE","text_ar":"نَبْع"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K, TA;) because this is one of the trees of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabal","text_ar":"جَبَل"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b8-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The echo."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 472.)"}],"source_refs":["K","Mgh","S","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n4981","headword_ar":"جَبُلٌ","root":"jbl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibil~N","text_ar":"جِبِلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n4982","headword_ar":"جَبِلٌ","root":"jbl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabolN","text_ar":"جَبْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  Also, applied to the iron head, or blade, of an arrow, or of a spear, or of a sword, &c., (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Blunt; that will not penetrate into a thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-' Abbád, K, * TA:) and so, with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":", applied to a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA^os","text_ar":"فَاْس"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n4983","headword_ar":"جُبُلٌ","root":"jbl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibil~N","text_ar":"جِبِلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n4988","headword_ar":"جُبُلٌّ","root":"jbl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see what next follows."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n4989","headword_ar":"جِبِلٌّ","root":"jbl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jubul~N","text_ar":"جُبُلٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibolN","text_ar":"جِبْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[accord. to the CK like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EadolN","text_ar":"عَدْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but correctly like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EidolN","text_ar":"عِدْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jubolN","text_ar":"جُبْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jubulN","text_ar":"جُبُلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) accord. to different readings of the instance occurring in the Kur xxxvi. 62, the first being the reading of the people of ElMedeeneh, (S,) [and the most common,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A great company of men;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibil~apN","text_ar":"جِبِلَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabiylN","text_ar":"جَبِيلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or [simply]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a company of men;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabulN","text_ar":"جَبُلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to Kh; (Sgh, TA;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabolapN","text_ar":"جَبْلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jubolapN","text_ar":"جُبْلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibil~apN","text_ar":"جِبِلَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": which last three signify also the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^um~apN","text_ar":"اُمَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a nation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]: (K:) it is said [by some] that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibil~N","text_ar":"جِبِلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is pl. [or coll. gen. n.] of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibil~apN","text_ar":"جِبِلَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a numerous company:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibalapN","text_ar":"جِبَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibolN","text_ar":"جِبْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qabaHa A@ll~`hu jibalatakumo","text_ar":"قَبَحَ ا@للّٰهُ جِبَلَتَكُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God remove far from prosperity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"success,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"your companies:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibalN","text_ar":"جِبَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibolapN","text_ar":"جِبْلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Bd in xxxvi. 62.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA","Fr"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}